    "attributes": {
        "action": "Decriminalise self-defence by any means against sexual assault ",
        "additional_details": "We believe the current legal framework for self-defence is failing victims of sexual assault.",
        "background": "Reform self-defence laws to ensure anyone resisting an attempted sexual assault can use any means necessary. The law must recognise that using a tool to stop a larger attacker is a proportionate and lawful act of prevention.",
